{"tid":84372,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人一聽到「外國人」呢個term，就自然會聯想起鬼佬？","createTime":"2017-01-17T13:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T04:47:47.000Z","uid":34701,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"30fdb1ac8132c33b5819c003783ea51cadfd8932","tid":84372,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:08:55.000Z","msg":"唔知點解喺我心目中，一講起「外國人」，心入面嘅畫面就一定係金頭髮白皮膚同講英文嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ne.g.如果有人同我講佢識到個外國fd，我就一定會第一時間覺得係鬼仔/妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算亞洲其他國家好似日本泡菜嗰啲都係外國嘅人，但第一時間一定係諗到西方國家嘅人先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人都係咁？"},{"pid":"3d5a87cd0c0ea4eef1402c492b68209d8c01bfa1","tid":84372,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:12:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63169a35194755806a74339a0551e135754830ec","tid":84372,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:31:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06fc9aae25ca5a0f78d82bfca53ef6e1002bfff","tid":84372,"uid":66909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:33:55.000Z","msg":"會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9874877f43efb07dd5bb44583e62d634d63ba1f3","tid":84372,"uid":32263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:35:23.000Z","msg":"外國人=英文人"},{"pid":"0f53c18ab4e1935d5893ad33190d64a03b6b9181","tid":84372,"uid":5736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:39:41.000Z","msg":"我都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能以前細個以為講英文就係西方人<br />\n久而久之就有perception <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da7dbe92c382642f3d6c1cccba1e9fc06cce9f9b","tid":8437